{"tid":722162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"冇嘢呀！要美斯日日瞓喺C朗隔離！","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T15:40:22.000Z","uid":4661,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00e630da7e4e8e5ccc2c825f85599bf878dbb514","tid":722162,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629164052102-0629_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180629164331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629164052102-0629_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180629164331&h=ab6c6b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷驚險出線，16強將要轉戰喀山面對法國，呢場波本來已經惡踢，點知大軍入住嗰間Ramada酒店對面，好衰唔衰有幢大廈成幅外牆，竟然有幅超巨型嘅C朗塗鴉，仲七彩斑爛鬼咁搶眼，美斯可以話瞓醒望出窗，就會見到呢個死敵喺隔離。就算拉埋晒窗簾，美斯離開酒店去練波，都冇可避免要同C朗「打招呼」，認真篤眼篤鼻。 <br />\n<br />\n唔可以換酒店咩？唔得！因為喀山只得兩間酒店有特許權接待世盃球隊，其中一間Mirage已經畀法國訂咗，事關「高盧雞」喺喀山對過澳洲踢分組賽，一早落定Booking，阿根廷根本冇得揀，唔住Ramada就惟有瞓街。老實講，美斯日日見到C朗，心情唔慌靚，呢個大整蠱都唔知係咪法國佬搞出嚟嘅。"},{"pid":"cabb5c5ff0d2af29e5bae5be877fccd1ac1aed30","tid":722162,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"比哂下台階你亞軍停 到時咪有藉口賴休息唔夠豬波"},{"pid":"43f1b876336ef1e45adf6f7062963d789785fb38","tid":722162,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"阿根廷首名出線就冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我認為冇得怪法國既。<br />\n<br />\n佢地根本FRIEND底，而且美斯心理狀況好好，唔會嬲嬲既。"},{"pid":"7d1ed6d08362b119458588d7f61b8369e82d566a","tid":722162,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:22:2